<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1919-01-09T07:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1919-01-09T07:00:00-05:00" n="289" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d289">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">Paris Peace Conf. 873.00/15:
                            Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Italy</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Page</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to
                                the <gloss type="to">Commission to Negotiate Peace</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Rome</hi>
                                </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-01-09T13:00:00+01:00">January 9, 1919—1 p.m.</date>
                                <lb/> [Received January 10—12:10 a.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>61. The following telegram from Cattaro was received yesterday by the
                            Minister of Marine here.</p>
                        <quote rend="blockquote">
                            <p>“January 8th. Insurgents urgently ask for the arrival of Italian
                                [apparent omission]. They have determined to resist to the last.
                                Period of ultimatum given by French General ends tomorrow evening.
                                His orders prevent our troops from being moved.”</p>
                        </quote>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Nelson Page</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>